Quote:  Fagus <i>Menziesii</i>, Hook. fil. ... HAB. Mountains of the Northern and Middle Islands. ... Nat. name, `Tawai', Col. `Red Birch' of the colonists. ... A very handsome tree, 80-100 feet high, ... <i>Bark </i>silvery, outer layers peeling off and exposing a red surface.
